Vice President Joe Biden and Energy Secretary Steven Chu are scheduled to make a major funding announcement regarding the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act of 2009. Secretary Chu will be visiting Solyndra, Inc. in Fremont, California, while Vice President Biden will deliver remarks via satellite. The event will include company representatives, elected officials, and a tour of the Solyndra Inc. facilities. The announcement is set to take place on Friday, September 4th at 9:00 AM PDT/12:00 PM EDT. For more information, contact the Department of Energy.